# /mnt/config/mbsyncrc (abandoned — see mail-sync.md)

IMAPAccount myaccount
Host mail.example.com
User mailuser
PassCmd "cat /mnt/secret/password.conf"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore myaccount-remote
Account myaccount

MaildirStore myaccount-local
Inbox /mnt/mail/account
SubFolders Maildir++
# Maildir++ uses dot-prefix: .Sent .Drafts .Trash etc

Channel myaccount
Far :myaccount-remote:
Near :myaccount-local:
Patterns *
Create Near
Remove None
Expunge None
SyncState /mnt/mail/metadata/myaccount/
Sync Pull
# Pull = readonly equivalent (never pushes changes to remote)
